a> rating in kWh/100 miles for the 2009 <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org=
/wiki/Mini_E" title=3D"Mini E">Mini E</a></div></div></div><div class=3D"tr=
ow"><div class=3D"tsingle" style=3D"width:222px;max-width:222px"><div class=
